OL,5,G0105 Wentworth Prison
OL,6,     FVera makes a dangerous plan to
OL,7,     Fbring down Ferguson, while Lou is
OL,8,     Fon the warpath and is out for
OL,9,     Fblood.
OL,10,G0205 Wentworth: The Final Sentence
OL,11,     FAfter a near fatal stabbing of
OL,12,     FAllie returns to Wentworth
OL,13,     Fgrappling with permanent injuries.
OL,14,     FMeanwhile, Ferguson finds it
OL,15,     Fincreasingly difficult to control
OL,16,     Fher desire for revenge.
OL,17,G0310 Wentworth: The Final Sentence
OL,18,     FDetermined to find out who killed
OL,19,     FReb, Lou finds herself comforted
OL,20,     Fby Marie, not realising Marie's
OL,21,     Fpart in the conspiracy, and that
OL,22,     FReb's killer pays with their life.
